hadiths[9]{hadithnumber,text}:
2295,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya main tumhen sab sey achey gawah key barey mein na bata dun? sab sey achcha gawah wo aadmi hai jo gawahi talab kiye janey sey pehley gawahi dey '' padhi. .
2296,"usi jaisi hadees marvi hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- aksar logon ney apni riwayat mein Abdur-Rehman bin abi Umra kaha hai. 3- is hadees ki riwayat karney mein Malik key shagirdon ka ikhtilaf hai, baaz raawiyon ney isey abi Umra sey riwayat kya hai, aur baaz ney ibne-Abi Umra sey, unka naam Abdur-Rehman bin abi Umra Ansari hai, ibne-Abi Umra ziyada sahih hai, kyonkey Malik key siwa doosrey raawiyon ney عن عبدالرحمٰن بن أبي عمرة an زيد بن خالد kaha hai عن ابن أبي عمرة an زيد بن خالد ki sanad sey uskey ilawa dusri hadees bhi marvi hai, aur wo sahih hadees hai, abu-Umrah Zaid bin Khalid Johni key azad karda ghulam they, aur Abu-Umrah key wastey sey Khalid sey hadees ghulul marvi hai, aksar log Abdur-Rehman bin abi Umra hi kehtey hain padhi. ."
2297,unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' sab sey behtar gawah wo hai jo gawahi talab kiye janey sey pehley apni gawahi ka fariza ada kar dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai.
2298,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''khayanat karney waley mard aur aurat ki gawahi durust aur maqbool nahin hai, aur na un mardon aur aurton ki gawahi maqbool hai jin par had nafiz ho chuki hai, na apney bhai sey dushmani rakhney waley ki gawahi maqbool hai, na us aadmi ki jiski eik baar jhooti gawahi aazmai ja chuki ho, na us shakhs ki gawahi jo kisi key zere-kafalat ho us kafeel khandan key haq mein (jaisay mazdoor waghera) aur na us shakhs ki jo wala ya rishte-daari ki nisbat mein muttahim ho''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Yazeed bin Ziyad Dimashqi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Yazeed zaeeful-Hadis hain, neez ye hadees Zohri ki riwayat sey sirf isi tareeq sey jaani jati hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr sey bhi hadees marvi hai, 4- Fazari kehtey hain : « قانع » sey murad « tabey » hai, 5- is hadees ka matlab hum nahin samajhtey aur na hi sanad key aetbar sey ye merey nazdik sahih hai, 6- is barey mein ehle-ilm ka amal hai ke rishtedaar key liye rishtey ki gawahi durust hai, albatta betey key haq mein baap ki gawahi ya baap key haq mein betey ki gawahi key barey mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, aksar ehle-ilm betey key haq mein baap ki gawahi ya baap key haq mein betey ki gawahi ko durust nahin samajhtey , 7- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : jab gawahi deney wala aadil ho to baap ki gawahi betey key haq mein isi tarah baap key haq mein betey ki gawahi durust hai, 8- bhai ki gawahi key jawaz key barey mein ikhtilaf nahin hai, 9- isi tarah rishtedaar key liye rishtedaar ki gawahi mein bhi ikhtilaf nahin hai, 10- Imam Shafai kehtey hain : jab do aadmiyon mein dushmani ho to eik key khilaf doosrey ki gawahi durust na hogi, bhaley hi gawahi deney wala aadil ho, unhoney Abdur-Rehman Aaraj ki hadees sey istidlaal kya hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan marvi hai ke dushmani rakhney waley ki gawahi durust nahin hai, isi tarah is (mazkura ( hadees ka bhi mafhoom yehi hai, (jis mein) aap ney farmaya : '' apney bhai key liye dushmani rakhney waley ki gawahi durust nahin hai ''."
2299,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khutba key liye khadey huye aur farmaya : ''logo! jhooti gawahi Allah key sath shirk karney key barabar hai, phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye aayat padhi فاجتنبوا الرجس من الأوثان واجتنبوا قول الزور '' to buton ki gandagi sey bachey raho ( un ki parastish na karo (aur jhoot bolney sey bachey raho '' ( Haj : 30) . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Sufiyan bin Ziyad ki riwayat sey jantey hain. aur logon ney Sufiyan bin Ziyad sey is hadees ki riwayat karney mein ikhtilaf kya hai, 3- neez hum aiman bin Khurem ka Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey samaa, bhi nahin jantey hain."
2300,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Fajr padhaai , jab paltey to khutba key liye khadey huye aur farmaya : '' jhooti gawahi Allah key sath shirk karney key barabar hai'' , aap ney ye baat teen martaba dohrai phir aap ney ye mukammal aayat tilawat farmaai (واجتنبوا قول الزور) '' aur jhooti baat sey ijtinab karo ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees merey nazdik ziyada sahih hai, 2- Khurem bin Fatik ko sharfe-sahabiyat hasil hai, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey unhoney kaee hadisein riwayat ki hain, aur mashhoor Sahabi hain."
2301,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' kya tumhen badey badey ( kabira ( gunahon key barey mein na bata dun? '' Sahaba ney arz kya : kyon nahin ? Allah key Rasool ! aap ney farmaya : '' Allah key sath shirk karna , maan-baap ki nafarmani karna aur jhooti gawahi dena ya jhooti baat bolna'' , abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aakhiri baat ko barabar dohraatey rahey yahan tak ke hum logon ney dil mein kaha : kaash! ! aap khamosh ho jatey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadees aai hai."
2302,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : '' sab sey achey log merey zamaney key hain ( yani Sahaba ( , phir wo log jo unkey baad ayengey (yani Tabe-een) , phir wo log jo unkey baad ayengey ( yani tabaa Tabe-een) padhi. , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ye baat teen martaba dohrani, phir unkey baad aisey log ayengey jo mota hona chahengey, motapa pasand kerengey aur gawahi talab kiye janey sey pehley gawahi dengey''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Aamash key wastey sey Ali bin mudrik ki riwayat sey gharib hai, 2- Aamash key deegar shagirdon ney عن الأعمش an هلال بن يساف an عمران بن حصين ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai."
2303,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' sab sey achey aur behtar log hamarey zamaney waley hain, phir wo log jo unkey baad hongey, phir wo log jo unkey baad hongey, phir jhoot aam ho jaeyga yahan tak ke aadmi gawahi talab kiye baghair gawahi dega, aur qism khilaaey baghair qism khayega''. aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wo hadees ke sab sey behtar gawah wo hai, jo gawahi talab kiye baghair gawahi dey to uska mafhoom hamarey nazdik ye hai ke jab kisi sey kisi chiz ki gawahi (haq baat ki khatir) dilwai jaey to wo gawahi dey, gawahi deney sey baaz na rahey, baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik dono hadeeson mein tatbeeq (yaksaniyat) ki yehi surat hai."
